Because that's what people do.

1459
01:49:24,975 --> 01:49:28,342
They leap and hope to God they can fly.

1460
01:49:34,184 --> 01:49:35,412
Because otherwise...

1461
01:49:36,520 --> 01:49:39,045
we just drop like a rock...

1462
01:49:39,723 --> 01:49:41,554
wondering the whole way down:

1463
01:49:42,526 --> 01:49:46,018
"Why in the hell did I jump?"

1464
01:49:47,798 --> 01:49:51,461
But here I am, Sara, falling.

1465
01:49:52,436 --> 01:49:56,566
And there's only one person
that makes me feel like I can fly.

1466
01:49:58,975 --> 01:50:00,135
That's you.

1467
01:50:05,482 --> 01:50:08,110
So, you kind of like me?

1468
01:50:09,186 --> 01:50:10,278
No.

1469
01:50:11,455 --> 01:50:12,615
I love you.

1470
01:50:13,990 --> 01:50:16,322
I love you, and I knew it from the first...

1471
01:50:26,970 --> 01:50:29,666
If I say it back now, it'll sound so stupid.

1472
01:50:32,843 --> 01:50:37,041
This is the guy I was telling you about.
Hitch, that's my sister, Maria.

1473
01:50:37,147 --> 01:50:38,944
And that's her husband, Tom.

1474
01:50:43,487 --> 01:50:44,749
Her husband.

1475
01:51:26,530 --> 01:51:27,997
Where's your date?

1476
01:51:28,565 --> 01:51:30,089
Don't have one.

1477
01:51:35,972 --> 01:51:37,701
I know. Shocking, huh?

1478
01:51:41,211 --> 01:51:43,941
Oh, my God!

1479
01:51:50,954 --> 01:51:52,182
Are you all right?

1480
01:51:53,823 --> 01:51:55,313
Grandma, what happened?

1481
01:51:55,825 --> 01:51:59,124
This young lady just saved my life.

1482
01:52:03,867 --> 01:52:05,960
Ask her to dance.

1483
01:52:07,237 --> 01:52:09,432
Well, if you insist.

1484
01:52:10,574 --> 01:52:13,566
- I'm Casey.
- Charles Wellington.

1485
01:52:14,844 --> 01:52:17,972
- And this...
- Forget it. Just go.

1486
01:52:31,595 --> 01:52:33,290
Basic principles:

1487
01:52:34,698 --> 01:52:35,858
There are none.
